properties.full_name: Great Petition artwork_type sculpture tourism artwork description Large-scale sculpture unveiled in December 2008 to celebrate the 100th anniversary of women's right to vote in Victoria. The sculpture is a white scroll-like structure, which is twenty metres long and imposing on the small reserve. start_date 2008-12 artist_name Susan Hewitt;Penelope Lee
